Overview

Synchrony is explored here through pairwise pearson correlations betweeen trees.

rings_field <- read.csv("Processed Data/matched_rings_field.csv") %>% 
  group_by(tree.uniqueID) %>% 
  mutate(minyear=min(Year)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% as.data.frame()

Synchrony

Distribution of pairwise pearson correlations between tree ring series broken down by species and site (based on fss detrended series).
